At Glass Concierge we specialize in high end glass repairs of all kinds along with the custom engraving services we offer. Here is a customer’s broken @toro_glass 7/13 that broke at the joint including part of the 90 degree arm. We repaired it by reconstructing the arm along with adding a thicker reinforced 18mm joint that is now stronger than ever!
